# .gitignore for .NET Worker Service (background service, PostgreSQL backend)

### Build output ###
bin/
obj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
[Xx]64/
[Xx]86/
[Bb]uild/

### IDE / editor files ###
.vs/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

### Rider ###
.idea/
*.sln.iml

### NuGet ###
# Skip this section entirely if using PackageReference only (default for SDK-style projects)
# Only relevant if you have a legacy packages.config
*.nupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

### Logs and runtime artifacts ###
*.log
logs/

### Secrets / environment-specific config ###
# Commit appsettings.json with placeholder values only.
# Exclude any file that might contain a real PostgreSQL connection string.
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.json
!appsettings.Development.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.key
*.env
.env

### OS files ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db